00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:47,790
Su Wuming.

588
00:23:48,470 --> 00:23:50,400
What is the 60th birthday funeral?

589
00:23:51,950 --> 00:23:53,270
It means that

590
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,190
when an elderly

591
00:23:55,230 --> 00:23:57,150
passes their 60th birthday,

592
00:23:57,350 --> 00:23:59,060
they'll have to enter

593
00:23:59,350 --> 00:24:01,510
a tomb built in advance.

594
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:04,110
This custom was born

595
00:24:04,140 --> 00:24:06,510
from the ancient times of hardship.

596
00:24:06,540 --> 00:24:08,760
Later, in chaotic times

597
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:11,110
when food and clothes were scarce,

598
00:24:11,950 --> 00:24:14,310
to let their children and grandchildren

599
00:24:14,430 --> 00:24:15,630
survive,

600
00:24:16,150 --> 00:24:18,000
the elderly would willingly

601
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:21,710
or be forced to enter the tomb.

602
00:24:22,470 --> 00:24:24,710
What Mr. Su said is

603
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,880
an earthern jar tomb or a death cellar,

604
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:30,510
a tomb that's not sealed off.

605
00:24:31,710 --> 00:24:33,420
When an elder goes in,

606
00:24:33,590 --> 00:24:36,430
their descendants deliver food every day.

607
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:37,910
They also

608
00:24:38,020 --> 00:24:39,410
have to bring a brick.

609
00:24:39,690 --> 00:24:41,590
Each time when they leave, they've to place a brick

610
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:43,120
at the entrance of the tomb,

611
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:45,070
until the tomb

612
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,470
is sealed shut.

613
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:48,920
My family's custom

614
00:24:49,110 --> 00:24:51,030
has long changed in Shazhou.

615
00:24:51,510 --> 00:24:53,030
Tomorrow, I'm going to

616
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:55,960
a cave that has been dug beforehand.

617
00:24:56,670 --> 00:24:58,330
But it's a prosperous era now.

618
00:24:58,390 --> 00:24:59,600
Why should you still

619
00:24:59,630 --> 00:25:01,110
follow such a family custom?

620
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:01,990
Tradition

621
00:25:02,510 --> 00:25:04,440
has nothing to do with prosperity.

622
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:05,990
As a Cao descendant,

623
00:25:06,390 --> 00:25:07,670
I must abide by it.

624
00:25:08,350 --> 00:25:10,190
Such a dehumanizing custom

625
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:11,420
isn't tradition.

626
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,610
Just abandon it.

627
00:25:14,390 --> 00:25:14,830
Li Chi.

628
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,600
As a judicial adjutant,

629
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:18,550
can you bear to watch

630
00:25:18,750 --> 00:25:19,750
your father-in-law

631
00:25:19,750 --> 00:25:21,150
choose the path of death

632
00:25:21,390 --> 00:25:22,590
on his 60th birthday?

633
00:25:23,150 --> 00:25:24,790
I've opposed it before.

634
00:25:25,190 --> 00:25:26,470
But the Family Supervisory Committee

635
00:25:26,470 --> 00:25:27,230
rejected it.

636
00:25:27,670 --> 00:25:29,070
Supervisory Committee?

637
00:25:29,350 --> 00:25:30,470
They're the

638
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:31,630
Cao family members

639
00:25:31,630 --> 00:25:33,960
who supervise the 60th birthday funeral.

640
00:25:34,430 --> 00:25:35,270
Governor Zhang.

641
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:35,930
Sheriff Lu.

642
00:25:36,910 --> 00:25:38,550
This is an internal affair

643
00:25:38,710 --> 00:25:39,830
of the Cao family.

644
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:42,360
It has nothing to do with the governor.

645
00:25:42,870 --> 00:25:45,070
Besides, I've made up my mind.

646
00:25:45,310 --> 00:25:46,910
I won't betray my ancestors.

647
00:25:48,950 --> 00:25:50,350
I believe in Buddhism.

648
00:25:50,820 --> 00:25:52,220
After entering the cave,

649
00:25:52,580 --> 00:25:53,720
I won't eat or drink,

650
00:25:53,910 --> 00:25:55,230
chanting sutras

651
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:57,000
and renouncing the world.

652
00:25:57,870 --> 00:25:58,730
Think about it.

653
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,790
Isn't this a way

654
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,790
to be emancipated

655
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:04,190
from death?

656
00:26:04,870 --> 00:26:07,290
Others don’t know of such joy.

657
00:26:11,300 --> 00:26:12,360
All this talk about

658
00:26:12,390 --> 00:26:14,550
the 60th birthday funeral has ruined the mood.

659
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,670
Time flies.

660
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:17,550
How fleeting.

661
00:26:18,150 --> 00:26:20,310
As stated in the Orchid Pavilion Preface,

662
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,990
The things you liked in the past

663
00:26:21,990 --> 00:26:23,250
have become old relics

664
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,870
in a blink of an eye.

665
00:26:25,670 --> 00:26:26,750
As the old saying goes,

666
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:28,390
death is a big deal after all.

667
00:26:28,870 --> 00:26:29,930
Of course it's sad.

668
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:32,150
But the joy still remains.

669
00:26:32,910 --> 00:26:34,030
Just like tonight,

670
00:26:34,150 --> 00:26:35,550
I have many friends here,

671
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,500
with the bright moon is in the sky.

672
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:38,910
Such is my life;

673
00:26:39,350 --> 00:26:41,030
what else can I ask for?

674
00:26:43,150 --> 00:26:43,610
Come on.

675
00:26:44,030 --> 00:26:46,230
Let me propose a toast to all of you.

676
00:26:55,630 --> 00:26:56,300
Mr. Cao.

677
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:58,050
Since I've met you,

678
00:26:58,910 --> 00:27:00,170
you're my dear friend.

679
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:02,110
I saw you

680
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:04,950
giving alms at the door.

681
00:27:06,630 --> 00:27:08,660
You are such a kind person.

682
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,950
After hearing your speech,

683
00:27:11,910 --> 00:27:14,390
I'm deeply impressed.

684
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:18,400
I already think of you as a dear friend.

685
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:20,370
I never thought...

686
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:24,750
this meeting is also a farewell.

687
00:27:25,830 --> 00:27:27,240
Mr. Cao!

688
00:28:48,710 --> 00:28:49,710
Assassin!

689
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:51,930
Catch the assassin!

690
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:27,990
He escaped.

691
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:30,790
Assassin?

692
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:33,390
An assassin came to Qiande Hall?

693
00:29:33,950 --> 00:29:34,830
I'm so sorry

694
00:29:34,900 --> 00:29:36,220
for startling you.

695
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:46,910
Fed is drunk.

696
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,430
You brought him

697
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:52,350
to the main room upstairs.

698
00:29:52,950 --> 00:29:54,830
That main room...

699
00:29:56,470 --> 00:29:57,470
I often

700
00:29:57,470 --> 00:29:59,280
sleep in that room.

701
00:30:01,830 --> 00:30:04,270
Whenever I get drunk in Qiande Hall,

702
00:30:04,390 --> 00:30:05,830
I rest there.

703
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:06,880
I don't want to

704
00:30:06,950 --> 00:30:09,750
disturb my family and servants by returning late.

705
00:30:10,670 --> 00:30:11,790
In that case,

706
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:14,910
the assassin was targeting Mr. Cao.

707
00:30:16,950 --> 00:30:18,110
I have never

708
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,790
offended anyone in my life.

709
00:30:20,710 --> 00:30:21,780
Mr. Cao,

710
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:24,630
you're the richest man in Shazhou

711
00:30:24,710 --> 00:30:27,240
and about to have your 60th birthday funeral.

712
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:29,070
It must involve

713
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:31,190
your family inheritance.

714
00:30:35,710 --> 00:30:37,310
You mean it's a family member

715
00:30:37,630 --> 00:30:38,760
who wants to harm me?

716
00:30:39,630 --> 00:30:40,910
It's just a guess.

717
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,550
Maybe the assassin

718
00:30:42,630 --> 00:30:44,030
was coming for us.

719
00:30:44,830 --> 00:30:46,430
This assassin was mediocre,

720
00:30:46,550 --> 00:30:47,610
a far cry from those

721
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,030
targeting you and Lu Lingfeng

722
00:30:49,030 --> 00:30:49,540
before.

723
00:30:49,910 --> 00:30:50,710
That's right.

724
00:30:50,910 --> 00:30:52,430
Not only is he unskilled in martial arts

725
00:30:52,430 --> 00:30:53,670
but also cowardly.

726
00:30:54,150 --> 00:30:55,110
When I woke up,

727
00:30:55,710 --> 00:30:56,950
the curved sword in his hand

728
00:30:56,950 --> 00:30:58,410
almost fell to the ground.

729
00:30:59,550 --> 00:31:00,350
Curved sword?

730
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:07,370
[Cao's Mansion]

731
00:31:09,150 --> 00:31:09,870
Who is it?

732
00:31:12,950 --> 00:31:13,630
Who is it?

733
00:31:19,310 --> 00:31:19,860
Father?

734
00:31:24,090 --> 00:31:25,490
Is Li Chi at home?

735
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:27,110
Isn't he with you

736
00:31:27,130 --> 00:31:29,110
entertaining guests at Qiande Hall?

737
00:31:29,110 --> 00:31:30,070
He's not home.

738
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:35,010
Don't lie to me.

739
00:31:39,710 --> 00:31:40,310
Father.

740
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:42,950
I'm your first child.

741
00:31:43,390 --> 00:31:44,390
Since I was young,

742
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:46,870
I did everything

743
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:48,190
you asked me to.

744
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,550
I married the man

745
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:51,670
you chose.

746
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:55,030
When did I ever lie to you?

747
00:31:58,380 --> 00:32:00,060
Fine.

748
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,360
Why are you crying?

749
00:32:02,070 --> 00:32:02,600
Alright.

750
00:32:03,110 --> 00:32:05,070
I'll go find him somewhere else.

751
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:07,080
Father, what's wrong with him?

752
00:32:10,830 --> 00:32:11,830
I-I mean...

753
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:14,280
did Li Chi

754
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,610
offend you?

755
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:19,190
I'll know after I find him

756
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:22,070
and interrogate him.

757
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:46,160
Get off your camel to leave the city!

758
00:32:59,430 --> 00:33:01,880
[Wangjing Gate]

759
00:33:07,310 --> 00:33:08,270
Cripple.

760
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:16,200
Who are you calling?

761
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,690
I am calling you.

762
00:33:28,270 --> 00:33:29,000
Minister Li.

763
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:29,800
Get lost!

764
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:30,760
It's really you.

765
00:33:31,030 --> 00:33:32,590
How was my sleeve arrow

766
00:33:32,950 --> 00:33:33,830
last night?

767
00:33:54,750 --> 00:33:55,670
Fed!

768
00:33:56,230 --> 00:33:57,990
You look like a beggar,

769
00:33:58,590 --> 00:34:00,590
yet you claim to be a miracle doctor.

770
00:34:00,950 --> 00:34:02,950
You disrespected me time and again.

771
00:34:03,670 --> 00:34:04,350
I, Li Chi,

772
00:34:05,230 --> 00:34:06,390
am a strong man.

773
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:07,740
After I got drunk,

774
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:09,949
I felt the urge to kill someone.

775
00:34:10,659 --> 00:34:11,460
Fortunately,

776
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:13,710
I stopped myself in time.

777
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,590
You're lying!

778
00:34:17,790 --> 00:34:18,449
Yesterday,

779
00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:20,389
I slept in Mr. Cao's room.

780
00:34:20,750 --> 00:34:22,219
You wanted to kill Mr. Cao.

781
00:34:22,830 --> 00:34:24,590
After you saw me in the bed,

782
00:34:24,610 --> 00:34:25,790
you changed your mind,

783
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:26,389
right?

784
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:28,760
Are you eyeing

785
00:34:29,310 --> 00:34:31,310
Mr. Cao's inheritance?

786
00:34:31,870 --> 00:34:32,429
You...

787
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:36,159
Father-in-law.

788
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:37,850
Don't listen to his nonsense.

789
00:34:38,060 --> 00:34:39,150
Your 60th birthday funeral

790
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,350
was imminent

791
00:34:41,139 --> 00:34:43,070
and I couldn't bear to say goodbye.

792
00:34:43,190 --> 00:34:44,659
I was already depressed.

793
00:34:45,190 --> 00:34:46,260
And this Chicken Fed

794
00:34:46,260 --> 00:34:47,739
kept picking on me.

795
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,570
I was drunk and wanted to

796
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:50,770
teach him a lesson.

797
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,960
But when I was about to do it,

798
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:53,760
I suddenly...

799
00:34:54,310 --> 00:34:55,550
became sober.

800
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,120
I regret it so much.

801
00:34:57,350 --> 00:34:59,100
I regret it so much!

802
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:02,430
Assassinating your father-in-law for the inheritance.

803
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:03,750
I think Physician Fed

804
00:35:03,750 --> 00:35:05,190
has a point.

805
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:07,090
If you were really wronged,

806
00:35:07,090 --> 00:35:08,550
you would've been cursing

807
00:35:08,750 --> 00:35:11,150
instead of patiently defending yourself.

808
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:17,580
What evidence do you have

809
00:35:18,750 --> 00:35:20,070
for your accusation?

810
00:35:21,350 --> 00:35:22,470
Lu Lingfeng.

811
00:35:23,230 --> 00:35:24,140
I heard

812
00:35:24,430 --> 00:35:25,950
you've solved some cases.

813
00:35:26,830 --> 00:35:27,590
Don't tell me

814
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,670
they were all based on speculation?

815
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:33,230
So what if I'm convicting you

816
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:34,550
on speculation?

817
00:35:36,750 --> 00:35:37,350
Nonsense!

818
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:39,990
How can we convict him

819
00:35:40,190 --> 00:35:41,350
without evidence?

820
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:51,910
I understand and sympathize

821
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,520
with Minister Li.

822
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:55,180
If I were him,

823
00:35:55,620 --> 00:35:57,590
a matrilocal husband

824
00:35:57,620 --> 00:35:59,250
who didn't get

825
00:35:59,290 --> 00:36:01,090
a fair share of the inheritance,

826
00:36:01,110 --> 00:36:02,150
I'd be indignant too!

827
00:36:02,150 --> 00:36:02,510
Yes!

828
00:36:02,810 --> 00:36:03,810
Even an outsider

829
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,170
can see this injustice!

830
00:36:14,110 --> 00:36:16,070
Is this still speculation?

831
00:36:16,950 --> 00:36:18,290
The governor

832
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:20,420
heard your confession.

833
00:36:26,870 --> 00:36:28,070
Father-in-law, I...

834
00:36:28,410 --> 00:36:30,140
It was in a moment of weakness.

835
00:36:30,470 --> 00:36:32,260
Let me ask you one thing.

836
00:36:34,240 --> 00:36:36,990
Does Cao Yin know about your assassination?

837
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:43,870
Say something.

838
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:49,850
Father, what's wrong with him?

839
00:36:50,870 --> 00:36:51,820
I mean...

840
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:54,110
did Li Chi

841
00:36:54,130 --> 00:36:55,270
offend you?

842
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,470
I'll know after I find him

843
00:36:59,710 --> 00:37:01,950
and interrogate him.

844
00:37:11,150 --> 00:37:12,150
Interrogate me?

845
00:37:12,910 --> 00:37:14,510
I'm the judicial adjutant.

846
00:37:14,830 --> 00:37:15,670
In Shazhou,

847
00:37:16,190 --> 00:37:18,070
only I can interrogate others.

848
00:37:28,770 --> 00:37:30,530
How did you hurt your leg?

849
00:37:31,270 --> 00:37:32,000
Stop asking.

850
00:37:32,910 --> 00:37:34,470
What did you do to my father?

851
00:37:35,580 --> 00:37:36,780
Go sleep with the kid.

852
00:37:36,990 --> 00:37:37,800
Li Chi!

853
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:40,300
Yin!

854
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:42,070
If you want my blood

855
00:37:42,070 --> 00:37:42,910
splattered all over you,

856
00:37:42,910 --> 00:37:44,110
keep brushing me off.

857
00:37:50,250 --> 00:37:50,890
Yin.

858
00:37:52,250 --> 00:37:53,750
I did all this

859
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:56,750
for you and Saisai.

860
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:59,040
Cao Yin is filial.

861
00:37:59,890 --> 00:38:00,690
She lied to you

862
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:02,230
that I wasn't home

863
00:38:02,530 --> 00:38:04,660
because she didn't want me to kill you.

864
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:05,650
She knows

865
00:38:06,250 --> 00:38:07,570
my curved sword

866
00:38:07,950 --> 00:38:09,270
has killed before.

867
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:11,560
How could you do such a thing?

868
00:38:12,730 --> 00:38:15,040
How can I live in this world?

869
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:17,390
Yin.

870
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:18,860
Don't be rash.

871
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:20,670
Think about it.

872
00:38:21,910 --> 00:38:23,260
For Saisai,

873
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:25,290
you can't do anything stupid.

874
00:38:30,860 --> 00:38:32,260
Let me bandage it for you.

875
00:38:32,620 --> 00:38:33,550
Go now.

876
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:34,470
Go?

877
00:38:34,710 --> 00:38:35,670
Go where?

878
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:36,640
Leave Shazhou.

879
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:37,930
You can hide anywhere.

880
00:38:37,960 --> 00:38:38,990
I'm an imperial official.

881
00:38:38,990 --> 00:38:40,390
How can I leave without permission?

882
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:42,390
So you do know you are an official?

883
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:44,680
As a judicial adjutant,

884
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:47,310
do you know how heavy a crime you've committed?

885
00:38:48,950 --> 00:38:50,680
Find a way to get out of the city.

886
00:38:50,950 --> 00:38:51,830
Come back

887
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:53,590
in a week or so after you've recovered.

888
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:54,320
By then,

889
00:38:54,490 --> 00:38:55,860
my father would be dead.

890
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:57,400
Sheriff Lu would

891
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:58,840
also have left Shazhou.

892
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:02,220
If anyone asks, tell them

893
00:39:02,660 --> 00:39:04,150
you were depressed tonight,

894
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,510
so you rode out of the city.

895
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:07,360
But you fell off the cliff, got injured,

896
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,690
and couldn't come back.

897
00:39:09,790 --> 00:39:11,990
Then, no one will hold you accountable.

898
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:13,870
Brilliant.

899
00:39:15,070 --> 00:39:15,990
Good idea.

900
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:20,030
My wife loves me the most.

901
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,160
You tried to kill my father.

902
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:26,320
I really want to make mincemeat of you!

903
00:39:28,790 --> 00:39:29,830
But my father will

904
00:39:30,350 --> 00:39:32,410
have his 60th birthday funeral soon.

905
00:39:33,230 --> 00:39:34,950
If you become a prisoner too,

906
00:39:36,030 --> 00:39:39,190
how will I and Saisai live?

907
00:39:42,430 --> 00:39:43,280
That means

908
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:44,750
Yin didn't know

909
00:39:45,750 --> 00:39:47,390
about your assassination.

910
00:39:54,350 --> 00:39:56,070
I'm sorry, Father-in-law.

911
00:39:57,740 --> 00:39:58,740
Please let me off.

912
00:39:58,950 --> 00:39:59,880
In the next life,

913
00:40:00,110 --> 00:40:01,190
I'll still be your son-in-law.

914
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:03,050
And continue to harm me in your next life?

915
00:40:03,050 --> 00:40:04,380
That's not what I meant.

916
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,230
I meant in my next life,

917
00:40:05,230 --> 00:40:06,230
I'll be your son-in-law.

918
00:40:06,230 --> 00:40:06,950
Shut up!

919
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:11,390
You are no longer my son-in-law.

920
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:13,120
Governor Zhang.

921
00:40:13,150 --> 00:40:14,880
Punish this villain severely.

922
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,710
Cao Zhongda!

923
00:40:24,470 --> 00:40:26,150
I'm an imperial official.

924
00:40:26,350 --> 00:40:27,550
I didn't kill anyone.

925
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,410
As a merchant,

926
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:33,190
how dare you ask for me to be punished severely?

927
00:40:34,810 --> 00:40:36,720
As a matrilocal husband,

928
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:39,360
I even let Saisai take the Cao surname.

929
00:40:40,140 --> 00:40:41,830
Why is the three of us only getting

930
00:40:41,830 --> 00:40:43,150
10% of the inheritance?

931
00:40:43,150 --> 00:40:44,150
10%!

932
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:45,110
I don't accept it!

933
00:40:45,110 --> 00:40:45,710
Wait.

934
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:51,640
My will

935
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:53,200
hasn't been announced yet.

936
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:55,250
How do you know the content?

937
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:01,670
It's Ding Mao, right?

938
00:41:02,910 --> 00:41:05,660
Your butler isn't loyal to you.

939
00:41:06,450 --> 00:41:07,550
To think you even made him

940
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:09,460
the provider of Cao Family Cave.

941
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:13,350
It took only five silver ingots.

942
00:41:17,390 --> 00:41:18,070
Master!

943
00:41:20,030 --> 00:41:20,470
Ding Mao.

944
00:41:20,470 --> 00:41:20,870
Master.

945
00:41:20,870 --> 00:41:21,670
Just in time.

946
00:41:22,870 --> 00:41:24,510
I trust you so much,

947
00:41:25,070 --> 00:41:26,950
but you are Li Chi's accomplice.

948
00:41:27,010 --> 00:41:28,470
Do you want to kill me

949
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:29,910
so that you can edit the will

950
00:41:29,910 --> 00:41:31,360
to get my inheritance?

951
00:41:31,390 --> 00:41:32,070
No!

952
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:34,270
I was just momentarily greedy.

953
00:41:34,270 --> 00:41:35,270
So I took his money

954
00:41:35,310 --> 00:41:37,010
and told him the content of the will.

955
00:41:37,010 --> 00:41:38,070
But I didn't expect

956
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,870
a judicial adjutant like him

957
00:41:39,870 --> 00:41:41,510
to try to kill you!

958
00:41:41,550 --> 00:41:42,880
I left the will with you,

959
00:41:42,990 --> 00:41:44,540
but you read it secretly.

960
00:41:45,180 --> 00:41:46,510
That's a serious crime.

961
00:41:47,750 --> 00:41:50,470
I'm guilty.

962
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:51,730
But Master,

963
00:41:51,950 --> 00:41:53,010
I'm here to tell you

964
00:41:53,190 --> 00:41:54,850
the servants at home reported

965
00:41:55,190 --> 00:41:56,390
that Young Master...

966
00:41:58,470 --> 00:41:59,990
He's dead.

967
00:42:10,780 --> 00:42:12,040
What nonsense is that?

968
00:42:13,030 --> 00:42:14,100
It's true.

969
00:42:15,670 --> 00:42:16,790
Young Master...

970
00:42:18,190 --> 00:42:20,790
He was murdered!

971
00:42:24,470 --> 00:42:25,060
Mr. Cao.

972
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,260
Duobao.
